@* 仕入先検索の検索結果(Ajax.BeginFormで検索結果だけ差し替えるため部分ビューにする) *@
@using PagedList.Mvc;
@using Resources = Wms.Areas.Master.Resources;
@model Wms.Areas.Master.ViewModels.VendorSearchModal.VendorSearchCondition

<h1>@Resources.SharedResource.VendorTitle</h1>
<br />
<ul class="sortarea">
    <li>
        @Resources.SharedResource.VendorIdSearch
        @Html.EditorFor(model => model.VendorId, new { htmlAttributes = new { @class = "w_6_short", @id = "txtVendorId", tabindex = "1" } })
    </li>
    <li>
        @Resources.SharedResource.VendorNameSearch
        @Html.EditorFor(model => model.VendorName, new { htmlAttributes = new { @class = "w_18_normal", @id = "txtVendorName", tabindex = "2" } })
        @Html.LikeMark(CommonsResource.Like)
    </li>
    <li>
        <div class="search">
            <button id="vendorSearch" type="button" class="btn btn-outline-dark" onclick="$('#frmVendorSearch').submit();">@FormsResource.BTN_SEARCH</button>
        </div>
    </li>
</ul>
<div class="message-area">
    @Html.Partial("_InformationMessageContent", TempData[AppConst.SUCCESS] ?? "")
    @Html.Partial("_ErrorMessageContent", TempData[AppConst.ERROR] ?? "")
</div>
@if (Model.VendorViewModel != null)
{
    <div class="sublbarea">
        <div class="sortarea">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    @FormsResource.DISPLAY_SHORT
                    <div class="sort">
                        <div class="sort_inner">
                            @Html.EnumDropDownListFor(m => m.SortKey, new { onchange = "$('#frmVendorSearch').submit();" })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sort">
                        <div class="sort_inner">
                            @Html.EnumDropDownListFor(m => m.OrderKey, new { onchange = "$('#frmVendorSearch').submit();" })
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="totalcount">
                    @String.Format(Share.Common.Resources.FormsResource.KENSU, Model.VendorViewModel.TotalItemCount.ToString("N0"))
                </li>
            </ul>
            @if (Model.VendorViewModel.Count() > 0)
            {
                @Html.PagedListPager(Model.VendorViewModel, Page => Url.Action("Index", new { Page, Model.VendorId, Model.VendorName, Model.SortKey, Model.OrderKey }), PagerHelper.GetOptions("vendorSearchResult", "vendorSearchModal.adjust();"))
            }
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="Container">
        <div>
            <div class="tb_scroll">
                <table class="table table-bordered">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th class="bg-grey w_checkbox"></th>
                            <th class="bg-grey">
                                No
                            </th>
                            <th class="bg-grey">
                                @Resources.SharedResource.VendorIdName
                            </th>
                            <th class="bg-grey">
                                @Resources.SharedResource.Vendor
                            </th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        @for (int i = 0; i < Model.VendorViewModel.Count(); i++)
                        {

                            var idx = (i + 1) + (Model.VendorViewModel.PageNumber - 1) * Model.VendorViewModel.PageSize;
                            <tr>
                                <td class="align-middle chk_cell">
                                    <label>
                                        @Html.RadioButton("SelectIndex", i.ToString(), new { @id = "VendorSelectIndex" + i.ToString(), @class = "radio_input" })
                                        <span class="radio_parts"></span>
                                    </label>
                                </td>
                                <td  class="text-right w_no">
                                    @idx
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorId)
                                    <br />
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorName1)
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorName2)
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorPrefName)
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorCityName)
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorAddress1)
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorAddress2)
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorAddress3)
                                </td>
                                <td class="template" hidden>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorId)
                                </td>
                                <td class="template" hidden>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorName1)
                                </td>
                                @Html.HiddenFor(model => model.VendorViewModel[i].Vendor.VendorId)
                            </tr>
                        }
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
}